      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_labour">Labour</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_clinical_intervention">CLINICAL INTERVENTION</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_labour">Labour</xref>
 is a period of time where there are painful contractions and changes to the cervix that result in the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_delivery">Birth</xref>
 of a baby and ending with the expulsion of the placenta and membranes.  </p>
